DATES TO REMEMBER

Festival Dates - April 11 -25th

Printed Program Books will be available at The Oriental Theatre!

IN PERSON BOX OFFICE STARTS APRIL 5th

ORIENTAL THEATRE

Box office opens one hour before the first screening and closes 20 minutes after the last screening starts.

DOWNER THEATRE

Box office opens one hour before the first screening and closes 20 minutes after the last screening starts.

AVALON THEATER / TIMES CINEMA

Box office opens one hour before the first screening and closes 20 minutes after the last screening starts.

MEMBERSHIP

Purchasing a Milwaukee Film Festival pass is an easy and fun way to support the nonprofit Milwaukee Film, one of our city's leading arts and culture organizations.

Members get the best prices plus year-round perks, and one pass is about the same price as a Milwaukee Film membership plus a Member pass!
